content: I'm actually really into self-help and personal development books right now. I find them really inspiring and motivating, and they've been helping me a lot on my journey to reduce my social media usage and focus on my own life. I just finished reading "The 7 Habits of Highly Effective People" by Stephen Covey, and I'm currently reading "Daring Greatly" by Brené Brown. I love her work and find her insights really thought-provoking.
